item.title: Omg click here if you own a working server ( moparscape )
item.dc:creator: @Hockey4lifexx Hockey4lifexx
item.description:
@Hockey4lifexx wrote:

click cancel and hit “start server” then try ur server on the default 127.0.0.1

then if it works go to ur run program and type in cmd, then type ipconfig into it.

next u will get ur ip and then u just go to www.no-ip.com and register. Click add host and make a server name u want ex) runescape.no-ip.biz

there u go type that in make sure ur “compiler AND run server” is working and bam u got a server[br][br][size=1]Posted on: December 24, 2007, 12:55:50 PM[/size][hr]go here too: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,195700.0.html
